Figure1b-d & Sfigure1a-c

Introduction

This is the script of making figure 1b-d and supplementary figure 1a-c including:

  1. NMDS plots showing relationships between immune cell traits and cytokine production upon stimulations traits. figure 1b,c & sfigure a-c

  2. Heatmap showing correlation between immnue cell counts and cytokine production upon stimulation. figure 1d

library(vegan)
library(ggplot2)

NMDS plots

Immnue cell proportion in 300DM:

dat<-read.table("~/Documents/working/projects/300DM/NMDS/cellcounts.txt",header=T,row.names=1,sep="\t",check.names = F,as.is = T)

nmds <- metaMDS(dat, k = 4)
summary(nmds)
nmds.species <- data.frame(nmds$species)

anno<-read.table("~/Documents/working/projects/300DM/NMDS/anno_cellcounts.txt",header=T,row.names = 1,sep="\t",check.names = F)

ol<-intersect(rownames(nmds.species),rownames(anno))
nmds.species<-nmds.species[ol,]

nmds.species<-transform(nmds.species,group=anno[ol,])

tmp<-nmds.species[c(1,5,6,7,8,9,10),]

nmds.species$group<-as.factor(nmds.species$group)

p=ggplot(data=nmds.species,aes(x=MDS1,y=MDS2,color=group))+geom_point()+scale_color_brewer(palette="Set1")+geom_point(data=tmp,size=5,aes(x=MDS1,y=MDS2))
p+stat_ellipse(lwd=0.5,linetype="dashed")+theme_bw()+theme(panel.border = element_blank())+xlab("First dimention of NMDS")+ylab("Second dimention of NMDS")

Heatmap

library(pheatmap)
library(RColorBrewer)
dat<-read.table("~/Documents/working/projects/300DM/correlation_cc_cyto/cellcounts.txt",header=T,row.names=1,sep="\t",check.names = F)
clean_data_number<-apply(dat,2,function(w) {tmp<-na.omit(w);length(tmp)})
keep<-which(clean_data_number>=0.2*nrow(dat))
clean_data<-dat[,keep] 
clean_data2<-na.omit(clean_data)
anno_cc<-read.table("~/Documents/working/projects/300DM/correlation_cc_cyto/anno_cellcounts.txt",header=T,row.names = 1,sep="\t",check.names = F)
clean_data2<-clean_data2[,rownames(anno_cc)]

mycol_CellSubpopulation=brewer.pal(9, c("Set1"))
names(mycol_CellSubpopulation)<-levels(anno_cc$group)

exp<-read.table("~/Documents/working/projects/300DM/correlation_cc_cyto/exp_for_cyto_mapping.txt",header=T,row.names = 1)

###fix the capital error
rownames(exp)[1]<-"Borreliamix_PBMC_7d_IFNy"

exp<-as.data.frame(t(exp))
anno<-read.table("~/Documents/working/projects/300DM/correlation_cc_cyto/anno.txt",header=T,row.names = 1,sep="\t")
anno<-anno[,-c(1,3)]

###fix the capital error
rownames(anno)[104]<-"Borreliamix_PBMC_7d_IFNy"

anno<-subset(anno,Stimus_Type!="RPMI" & Stimus_Type!="RPMIserum")
mycol_Stimulations=brewer.pal(5, c("Set2"))
mycol_Cytokine=c(brewer.pal(9,"Pastel1"),"aquamarine")
mycol_Time=c("pink","lightblue")
names(mycol_Cytokine)<-as.character(unique(anno$Cytokine))
names(mycol_Stimulations)<-as.character(unique(anno$Stimus_Type))
names(mycol_Time)<-as.character(unique(anno$Time))
annotation_colors<-list(Stimus_Type=mycol_Stimulations,Cytokine=mycol_Cytokine,Time=mycol_Time,Cell_Subpopulation=mycol_CellSubpopulation)

samples<-intersect(rownames(exp),rownames(clean_data2))
cc<-clean_data2[samples,]
cyto<-exp[samples,]

res<-matrix(NA,nrow=ncol(cc),ncol=ncol(cyto))
res<-as.data.frame(res)
rownames(res)<-names(cc)
names(res)<-names(cyto)
res_p<-res
for (c in rownames(res)){
  for (cy in names(res)){
    tmp<-data.frame(a=as.numeric(cc[,c]),b=cyto[,cy])
    t<-cor.test(as.numeric(tmp$a),tmp$b,method = "spearman") 
    r<-t$estimate[1]
    p<-t$p.value
    res[c,cy]<-r
    res_p[c,cy]<-p
  }
}

names(anno_cc)<-"Cell_Subpopulation"
col=colorRampPalette(c("blue","white", "tomato"))(16)
res<-res[rownames(anno_cc),]

tmp<-names(res)
tmp<-gsub(tmp,pattern = "_PBMC",replacement = "")
names(res)<-tmp
tmp<-rownames(anno)
tmp<-gsub(tmp,pattern = "_PBMC",replacement = "")
rownames(anno)<-tmp

pheatmap(res,cluster_rows = F,col=col,annotation_row = anno_cc,annotation_col = anno,annotation_colors = annotation_colors,breaks = seq(-0.4,0.4,0.05),legend_breaks = seq(-0.4,0.4,0.1),fontsize = 10,width = 10)
